props.content:
To make sure your Council Tax bill is correct, you need to tell us when you move from one address to another.

Portsmouth City Council will process your personal information appropriately and legally in accordance with the relevant national legislation.

The details you provide will be held in a secure system or database and will only be shared with other organisations where the law allows.

Follow the link for details of our data protection policy.

Before you complete this form

To help us ensure we calculate your bill correctly and send information to the correct address, please have ready:

  • Your new address
  • The date you are moving (or moved) to the new address
  • If moving to a Portsmouth address, details of other people at the new property

If you want to apply for a Council Tax discount or exemption (such as single person discount) follow the link for information on how to apply - don't complete this form.
